WEBVTT

00:00.023 --> 00:01.664
Previously on "Royal Pains"...

00:01.827 --> 00:03.311
Can we get a little help over here?

00:03.336 --> 00:04.577
Jen and Sam!

00:04.602 --> 00:07.561
Sam seems like such a great, happy kid,

00:07.562 --> 00:10.432
I don't want to cause collateral damage.

00:10.442 --> 00:11.552
I don't wanna be my dad.

00:11.562 --> 00:13.442
Sam's actually leaving next week

00:13.467 --> 00:15.352
to spend the summer in
Idaho with his dad.

00:15.392 --> 00:18.351
- Hi. Diana Underhill.
- Hank Lawson. Nice to meet you.

00:18.352 --> 00:20.422
I can't let anyone see me
dealing with a medical problem.

00:20.432 --> 00:21.542
Diana, I'm sorry to tell you,

00:21.552 --> 00:23.542
you may have to consider a hysterectomy.

00:23.552 --> 00:25.471
Can I get it all done at once?

00:25.472 --> 00:27.511
You mean do the
hysterectomy on the spot?

00:27.512 --> 00:29.352
I think I just wanna get it over with

00:29.362 --> 00:31.372
and get back to work.

00:31.382 --> 00:32.551
I have a Senate seat to win.

00:32.552 --> 00:34.472
Excuse me, we're looking for Dr. Sacani.

00:34.482 --> 00:36.352
Are we in the right place?

00:36.362 --> 00:38.472
Jeremiah, those patients over
there are waiting for you.

00:38.482 --> 00:40.481
Those aren't patients.
Those are my parents.

00:40.482 --> 00:42.472
I don't know why they're here,
but I'll ask them to leave.

00:42.482 --> 00:44.552
Hospital server's down.
No one's getting emails.

00:44.562 --> 00:46.422
I think this tech glitch

00:46.432 --> 00:47.512
is getting worse.

00:47.522 --> 00:50.361
You know that glitch? It's
not a technical problem.

00:50.362 --> 00:51.441
So then what's the issue?

00:51.442 --> 00:53.432
We've been hacked.

00:55.000 --> 01:01.074
